OL,6,FOpportunities to improve the
OL,7,Fresilience of the health system in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland ahead of the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic were lost because Stormont
OL,10,Fwas suspended for three years, Health
OL,11,FMinister Robin Swann has said.
