OL,6,F"So when it came to the steps we
OL,7,Fneeded to take during lockdown we
OL,8,Fcould have had some green-site
OL,9,Fhospitals already established in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, where we could have
OL,11,Fdesignated those for the procedures we
OL,12,Fneeded to do that were normal red-flag
